lead_paragraph: Rookie Jaccob Slavin scored in the fourth round of the shootout, and the Carolina Hurricanes beat the Ottawa Senators 4-3 on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Slavin, Skinner Help Carolina Beat Ottawa 4-3 in Shootout
